      "text": [
        " فِي نِصْفِ الْجَلْدَةِ وَ ثُلُثِ الْجَلْدَةِ يُؤْخَذُ بِنِصْفِ السَّوْطِ وَ ثُلُثَيِ السَّوْطِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "From him, from Ali Bin Al Hakam, from Hisham Bin Salim, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said regarding half the Lashing, and a third of the lashing: ‘He (the whipper) would grab by half (length of) the whip, and a third (length of) of the whip’."
